# LE-CRV

Forward-Secure Threshold Lamport Signatures via Lazy-Expanded Puncturable Seeds.

A post-quantum threshold signature library where a trusted dealer distributes
constant-size seeds instead of linear-size key shares, and past signing keys
become cryptographically unrecoverable after use.

## Install (development)

    python -m venv .venv
    .venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
    pip install -e ".[dev]"

## Run tests

    pytest

## Run benchmarks

    pytest benchmarks/ --benchmark-only
